snippet.textDisplay: As a pahadi ( from the Indian state of Uttarakhand ) this video made me realise that a lot of melodies, culture and dressing is common among the people from the mountains. Kashmiris, Himachalis and Uttarakhandi share a lot of dressing and cultural similarities, for example, the tune of the songs, the dressing and even the dances share a lot of commonalities, which I see even in this video. Hope to someday come to Pakistan and see this place first hand.
